
# mongodb
Image mongo db, using docker compose


# Using

`docker-compose up --build`

`docker-compose down`

`docker exec -it some-mongo bash`

`docker logs some-mongo`

# Using mongodb

http://0.0.0.0:8081/

# Acessing mongodb via Docker 

`docker exec -it database-mongodb_mongo_1 bash`

`mongo --username smanioto --password --authenticationDatabase admin` or `mongo`

# Acessing mongodb via MongoDBComprass (Instaled)

https://www.mongodb.com/products/compass

mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/mongo-api'

